1. Preparation
	1.1	Install Microsoft Visual Studio 2012
	1.2	Install InstallShield 
	1.3	Set up Perl environment.

2.	Build ADO.NET installer
	2.1	Modify the variables in buildinfo.bat as your own.
	2.2	Run buildinstaller.bat, then the installer will be under %build_dir%\installer

3.	Q&A
	3.1	Question: Why it build successful but I did not find the expected installer under expected folder %build_dir%\installer.
Answer: That might be the installer has another extension except EXE. Please try to find it in .%build_dir%\installer\PROJECT_ASSISTANT\ADO.NET\DiskImages\DISK1..


